    <h2 id="science">Why Creatine Is the Gold Standard for Muscle Growth</h2>

    <p>Creatine monohydrate is not a trend — it is the single most researched and validated sports supplement in human history. Over 500 peer-reviewed studies spanning three decades have consistently demonstrated that creatine supplementation at 3-5 grams daily increases muscle phosphocreatine stores, which allows you to perform more reps, lift heavier weights, and recover faster between sets. This enhanced training capacity translates directly into accelerated muscle growth over time.</p>

