      <summary>Do creatine gummies work for muscle growth?</summary>
      <p>Yes, if they deliver 3-5g of creatine monohydrate daily. Creatine is the most proven sports supplement with 500+ studies confirming increased strength, power, and lean mass. A 2022 meta-analysis found +3.1 lbs of lean muscle over 4-12 weeks of training with creatine vs placebo.</p>
